{"tid":941784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【慘被拉落水】淫監製Harvey Weinstein聲稱與珍妮花羅倫絲上床","createTime":"2018-12-15T06:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T15:37:47.000Z","uid":49391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e55eefe8d6f0bac96dbc397aea2f1b3dfa126e12","tid":941784,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181215/large/1544849225_f3ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181215%2Flarge%2F1544849225_f3ef.jpg&h=33d12a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n珍妮花羅倫絲近日再與Harvey Weinstein扯上關係。<br />\n前年爆出性醜聞嘅美國電影大亨Harvey Weinstein，近日再被一位匿名女星在洛杉磯入稟告性侵，女方指曾被迫遭Harvey Weinstein強行口交，對方更講：「我同珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）瞓過，睇佢現在上到去邊個位？仲啱啱攞埋奧斯卡！」原告人表示，與Harvey Weinstein是在2013年嘅辛丹斯電影節上認識，當時相約到酒店會面，之後女受害人到房間如廁，Harvey Weinstein亦有跟進房間，之後佢突然除褲自瀆，女方曾一度反抗，但Harvey Weinstein最後也在其裙上射精。相隔約兩年，Harvey Weinstein於2015年再次向女方性侵。<br />\n金像女星珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）再與Harvey扯上關係，曾發聲明鬧爆Harvey嘅珍妮花透過發言人表示：「我從來跟他沒有任何工作以外的關係，這是他對無數女性作出掠奪性策略及謊言的另一個例子。」開腔否認今次消息。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181215/59032781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032781&d=e1B%2BsLKjD6hnkCcKZdw5IwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=571397a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181215%2F59032781&h=e1c95fe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181215/59032781</a>"},{"pid":"9c77ceff24356686a95bde1f8486d51a109668ac","tid":941784,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444330feffaeccc